gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Mavericks 121, Rockets 115
gameRecap.excerpt: The Mavericks defeated the Rockets, 121-115, on their way to an 11-6 record and 2-2 in West B play. The Rockets move to 8-7 on the season and 2-2 in West B play. With the Mavericks win over the Rockets, the Pelicans have clinched West Group B and advance to the Knockout Rounds.
